author: @abhishekgalagali5968
text: fit_transform is used for learning the transformation parameters from the training data and applying the transformation to the same data. transform is used for applying a previously learned transformation (calculated from the training data) to new, unseen data. It assumes the transformation parameters are already available and fitted on the training data.
